== Flash support ==

In order to get flash support:

{{Emerge|www-plugins/adobe-flash| www-plugins/nspluginwrapper}}  
 
Execute the following command to get flash working in Epiphany (on 32 bit): 

<code>/usr/lib/nspluginwrapper/i386/linux/npconfig -v -a -n -i</code>.  

For 64 bit, change i386 in the previous command to x86_64.
